      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum mechanics assumptions justified for titanium alloy at quasi-static loading rates; contact formulation validated against known frictional sliding behavior.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model justified for Ti-6Al-4V at sub-yield loading; nonlinear geometry enabled to capture large-displacement bending response. Augmented Lagrange contact formulation selected based on prior validation studies. Isotropic material assumption confirmed appropriate by microstructural analysis. Gradation 3 achieved."
