      "rationale": "Testing performed strictly per ASTM F1717 at ambient conditions and a single displacement rate (5 mm/min). Only one test condition evaluated; no variation in loading rate, temperature, or simulated body fluid environment. This limits generalizability of the validation evidence. Required Gradation 3 not achieved; achieved Gradation 2. Noted as a credibility gap in the package description."
