      "rationale": "Systematic comparison table prepared mapping each FEA input to its experimental counterpart. Fixture geometry replicated in FEA from engineering drawings. Torque-controlled screw seating replicated via pretension element. No material or geometric surrogates used. Gradation 3 achieved."
