    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors. Twelve factors are assessed; eleven meet or exceed the required gradation level. Test conditions achieved only Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3, which is noted as a limitation but accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and inter-laboratory consistency. The package is accepted for the stated COU on the basis that the overall body of evidence is sufficient for a Medium assurance level decision.",
